## Additional Issues Worth Fixing

| Issue | Problem | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `SELECT *` | Fetches all columns; wastes I/O | Select only needed columns |
| No pagination | `SELECT * FROM users` returns entire table | Add `LIMIT`/`OFFSET` or cursor pagination |
| No query complexity limits | A deeply nested query can still DoS the DB | Use `graphql-depth-limit` or `graphql-query-complexity` |
| No field projection | Resolver ignores what fields were requested | Use `info.fieldNodes` to build a dynamic `SELECT` |
